{"tid":517774,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"垃圾學校 垃圾制度","createTime":"2018-01-02T15:34:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-03T07:47:17.000Z","uid":25046,"like":22,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"33a178ddf9ee88cb8e656b84e02c85f863692b49","tid":517774,"uid":25046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T15:34:11.000Z","msg":"真係好憎自己學校 完全唔講得上對學校有歸屬感 <br />\n到底學校幾時先肯改善制度？<br />\n跳橋又有試過 條友唔死 學校就唔理 到依加有人死左 肯改未？<br />\nRIP 到最後你死都希望為我地帶來改變 好偉大 多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fab0c85bf7b81393e95312033c05b045e6e2b535","tid":517774,"uid":141544,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T15:43:47.000Z","msg":"d垃圾校長要改一早改左啦 睇開啲啦"},{"pid":"b9122d6878cd44b85dbc40b16da10a68081e1ead","tid":517774,"uid":4316,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T15:45:18.000Z","msg":"紫色巨塔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cad0a31d4b85315d50d7ee90d4629a26431d14f","tid":517774,"uid":143787,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T15:46:34.000Z","msg":"屯門果間 定慈雲山果間<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw 我果間都好垃圾 成班老屎忽冇心教書 又冇料<br />\n仲用膠水茶係pat pat到 坐住張凳 踢撚極都唔走<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪要出左事 佢地先會正視問題<br />\n既然係咁 死開啦教畜 希望佢地有報應 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：屯門band2尾學校"},{"pid":"3818af59e7d420a804b68ad004bf949cb6c889c7","tid":517774,"uid":25046,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T15:52:21.000Z","msg":"同級同學 雖然唔熟 <br />\n但絕對唔會係我地抗逆低 <br />\n學校一直要面去保持所謂既排位<br />\n辛苦了同學們"},{"pid":"887163480c3485b7a9a24ef5e64d9471930e0234","tid":517774,"uid":143787,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T16:02:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同級同學 雖然唔熟 <br />\n但絕對唔會係我地抗逆低 <br />\n學校一直要面去保持所謂既排位<br />\n辛苦了同學們</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n梁球鋸？因為你講所謂既排位<br />\n 不論梁球鋸好 還是其他區學校<br />\n間間中學d老屎忽 為左交好成績<br />\n就迫d學生參加呢樣 參加果樣<br />\n但從來冇問過同學想唔想參加<br />\n攞左獎之後 學校成日係咁講個果獎有幾勁<br />\n大佬 咁樣咪比左壓力果學生lo<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e521179e61ef507a90a43b06e9d6b5f5dad00dc","tid":517774,"uid":47614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T16:05:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌個垃圾校長幾時死？弄權弄得好開心？"},{"pid":"874ba3ffffa16fe3bf706e9936f5cf6625442f9c","tid":517774,"uid":25046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T16:08:12.000Z","msg":"慈雲山一名17歲青年墮樓，送院後證實不治。<br />\n　　事發在下午5時許，一名青年由慈康邨康添樓高處墮下，重傷倒臥大廈對開，街坊見狀報警。他昏迷由救護車送往聯合醫院搶救，惜終告不治。"},{"pid":"351039dcb8ce4627d2d7cab00cfa8befe96b59d9","tid":517774,"uid":25046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T16:15:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌個垃圾校長幾時死？弄權弄得好開心？</blockquote><br />\n聽日返學幫你問下"},{"pid":"5d81b9d21c66f90ad168c18754143cd4c9b7b98e","tid":517774,"uid":139484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6cad0a31d4b85315d50d7ee90d4629a26431d14f","tid":517774,"uid":143787,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T15:46:34.000Z","msg":"屯門果間 定慈雲山果間<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw 我果間都好垃圾 成班老屎忽冇心教書 又冇料<br />\n仲用膠水茶係pat pat到 坐住張凳 踢撚極都唔走<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪要出左事 佢地先會正視問題<br />\n既然係咁 死開啦教畜 希望佢地有報應 <img src=\"/assets/faces/norma